OL,6,FPaedophile headteacher Neil Foden "ran
OL,7,Fa reign of terror" for "many years,"
OL,8,Fthe chair of a major review has said.
OL,10,FThe Child Practice Review into how
OL,11,FFoden was able to sexually abuse
OL,12,Fchildren for years was published
OL,13,Fyesterday (Tuesday, 4 November), and
OL,14,Fhighlighted more than 50 missed
OL,15,Fopportunities to intervene and stop
OL,16,Fthe abuse.
