OL,6,FFoden, now aged 68, is serving a 17-
OL,7,Fyear prison sentence for sexually
OL,8,Fabusing four girls over a four-year
OL,9,Fperiod, telling one she "must take it
OL,10,Fto the grave and not tell anyone".
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Cymru Wales, Jan
OL,13,FPickles OBE, independent chair of the
OL,14,FChild Practice Review panel said:
OL,15,F"What we saw was systemic failure. At
OL,16,Fall points across the system.
