OL,6,F"The safeguarding arrangements in
OL,7,FWales are very sound. I work across
OL,8,FEngland as well and I feel they're
OL,9,Fmore robust in Wales. They weren't
OL,10,Ffollowed.
OL,12,FBut Jan Pickles said that there had
OL,13,Fbeen failures right across the board,
OL,14,Fincluding the education department,
OL,15,Fchildren's services and the local
OL,16,Fauthority.
OL,18,F"It's gruelling to see that level of
OL,19,Fdetail, to see that level of failure.
OL,20,FIt's appalling."
