OL,6,FFoden, of Old Colwyn, was found guilty
OL,7,Fof 19 charges, including 12 of sexual
OL,8,Factivity with a child, at a trial
OL,9,Fwhich lasted almost four weeks in 2024.
OL,11,FIn addition, he was found guilty of
OL,12,Ftwo counts of sexual activity with a
OL,13,Fchild by a person in a position of
OL,14,Ftrust, one count of causing or
OL,15,Finciting a child to engage in sexual
OL,16,Factivity, attempting to arrange the
OL,17,Fcommission of a child sex offence,
OL,18,Fsexual communication with a child,
OL,19,Fpossessing indecent photographs of a
OL,20,Fchild for show, and the sexual assault
OL,21,Fof a child under 13.
