OL,6,FMs Pickles explained how the review is
OL,7,F'ten times bigger' than any they have
OL,8,Fever undertaken in Wales around
OL,9,Fsafeguarding.
OL,11,FShe said: "I'm very proud of it, I'm
OL,12,Fvery proud of how the victims have
OL,13,Fresponded to it. Although, it's even
OL,14,Fmore heartbreaking for them to see
